sourcesContent: import React from 'react' import styled from 'styled-components' import { Thumbnail, H2 } from './StyledElements' const Project = styled.div` ` const Img = styled(Thumbnail)` grid-area: img; height: 200px; ` const DemoLink = styled.a` ` const GitLink = styled.a` ` const Title = styled(H2)` ` const Technologies = styled.div` ` const Description = styled.div` ` export default function ProjectCard ({data}) { const {title, description, imageURL, liveLink, gitLink} = data; return ( {title} {description} ) }
